Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.09,0:00:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooo, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you OK, Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that entering the\NPonyville Paw-Kour contest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was a dangerous idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.83,0:01:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You just rest here and I'll have\Nyou all fixed up in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. I'm all out\Nof bunny foot braces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.07,0:01:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we need to pay\Na visit to Dr. Fauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure that she\Nwould be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is anypony there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Oh, am\NI glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could say the same,\Nbut the door is stuck so,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I um... can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Somebunny hurt his foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bandage that up\Nso he can get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to keep him overnight,\Nbut as you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,my place is just\Nbursting with animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can take in even\None more critter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have your\Nhooves full here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is like a zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, it's normally\Nlike that but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now does my favorite wittle\Nbunny want a carrot-pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's OK. I think the goats\Nate all of them, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe all these\Npoor little animals are hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flummoxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day, there's more and\Nmore animals on my doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them just\Nhave minor ailments:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,hurt wings, stuffy\Nnoses and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But the trouble is, even\Nafter they're all healed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to get these\Ncomfy critters to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They do seem to have made\Nthemselves right at home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why they chose\Nto flock to my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't\Nmake sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Dr. Fauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best Vet\NPony in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's what I've\Nbeen telling everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Do you suppose it's\Nmy fault? I'm so sorry;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean for\Nthis to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know animals feel safe\Nand happy under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I don't mind if a\Nsnake wants to slither in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or a raccoon needs a rest. But\Nnow this place is so full,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no space to treat\Nany injured animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm going to\Nfix for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have the\Nperfect solution
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll make the critters\Nhappy and give you more space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have all\Nyour ducks in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner you fix\Nit, the better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for rushing right\Nover when I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Fauna needs my help\Nwith a serious problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A friendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Her vet clinic is a\Nbit maybe um... overrun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with adorable critters in\Ndire need of a safe place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to lay their heads and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,... they don't have\Nanywhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Dr. Fauna's\Nalways fixin' Winona up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when she ain't\Nfeelin' too fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so helpin' her out\Nis A-OK by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great news because it\Nmeans you'll all be helping me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with something special, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that's been a dream\Nof mine for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goody! Is your dream\Nto make a bouncy castle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,shaped like a\Ngigantic bundt cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no...\Nnot exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it,\NFluttershy? Spill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to build a\Nreal animal sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful habitat where every\Nanimal, whether sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or even just lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Feathered or furry,\Nscaly or slimy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,every critter would be welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My sanctuary can be the\None place in Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they call home till they feel\Nready to take on the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard you speak\Nwith such conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was exquisite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all taught me so much\Nabout building my confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,over the years. It's\Nbecause of your friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that I finally feel able to make\Nmy dream project a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't build the sanctuary\Nalone. Will you join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to offer my\Nextra hooves to ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But come to think of it,\NI actually know a filly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd be more help than I\Nwould. She's a friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,from Winona's sheep herdin'\Ncompetition: Wrangler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an expert in\Nanimal enclosures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo! Ooo! Ooo! I\Nknow somepony, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard Hat is the best\Nconstruction pony in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He can build anything you\Ncould ever, ever, ever want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing you all\Nmention these experts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I am reminded that I,\Ntoo, have the perfect pony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to help capture the\Nessence of your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To give it some\Nstyle, some flair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it you, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Um I was referring to\Nthe premiere interior designer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Canterlot\NElite: Dandy Grandeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped me when I was setting\Nup my Canterlot boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he'd be thrilled\Nto work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, everypony!\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to meet all of\Nthem and hear their ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right on\Ntrack to building
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the most wonderful\Nsanctuary in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,\NRupert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. It's wonderful that\Nyou all could join me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to discuss the Ponyville\Nsanctuary project.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends have so\Nmany nice things to say
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,about each of your talents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big project,\Nso I'm happy to have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,such experienced ponies\Nworking on it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity has impeccable taste\Nin design and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't wait to work\Nwith you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I--I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just lookin' forward\Nto helpin' ya out, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh... Pinkie Pie said\Nyou drew up some blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Not exactly; it's\Nmore of a "dream-board."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure doesn't look\Nlike an animal hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's\Nnot. It's a sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A place that is safe but not\Nrestrictive, cozy but natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where the animals can\Ncome and go as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So... can you build it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the sanctuary to\Nhave an open floor plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No walls, more like an enclosure\Nthat melts into the trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with a gate in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, the animals\Ncan return to the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right when they feel ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaky! I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I designed\Nthe Ponyville Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I could do the exact\Nsame thing right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it'll take a while\Nto clear all these trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to clear the\Ntrees. I want to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're talking about\Ndoesn't really seem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,like a cohesive structure. Or\Nany structure I'm familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Critters don't live\Nthe same way ponies do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is unconventional,\Nbut that's because
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we're trying to do something\Nthat's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really believe\Nit'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. I'll\Nsee what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Fluttershy?\NWhatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she thinks\Nknows what's best,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but once she sees how\Nmuch better it works
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,with these plans,\Nshe'll thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like for\Nthe window treatments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving the print\Non those!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... not to be rude, but\Nthere must be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no need for\Ncurtains at the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And why ever not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to look\Nnatural in the animal habitats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.45,0:11:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,not like it was\Nmade for ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All those shades\Nof brown and green?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... they're so\Ndrab. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Drab? You're calling the colors\Nof beautiful trees drab?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! The "natural"\Nlook is not in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is better, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your input,\Nbut I just know the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,would be happiest with\Ndirt brown pillows
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and leaf green accents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When a client has a vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they need me to\Nsteer them away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if its dirt brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And right there we got yer\Nstandard sheep travelin' cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fits two critters,\Ndependin' on size.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, sugarcube?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for something\Nless like a cage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,more like a nice hug. Maybe\Nif we lose that part...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then it\Nwouldn't be a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the perfect\Nbase for a little nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a bunch of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And anything else the\Nanimals can burrow into.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't\Nwant something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,more secure for\Nthe critters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She does have a\Npoint there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want\Na bunny wandering
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,into the wrong\Ncave, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No cages. I want to\Ngive the animals the freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,to come and go. It's the only\Nway they'll feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you\Nthink, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you we'd be fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost finished with\Nthe building already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The color just pops,\Nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite roomy inside,\Nreally. And very safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep us\Nwaiting, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you love it or\Ndo you love it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I.. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't love it. This is\Nnot going to work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A giraffe can't fit\Nthrough this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With these curtains\Nblocking the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,how are the birds going\Nto sing in the sunshine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the\Nopposite of a nice hug!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you all\Nworked hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but none of you did\Nanything I asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! We used the\Ntrees just like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that curtain\Nfabric is organic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got\N"natural" fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I added pillows\Ninside my cages!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That should count as\Nfeelin' like a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not know much\Nabout construction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or interior design,\Nor wrangling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am an expert at one\Nthing: the care of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And what animals need is\Na sanctuary, not this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe your vision wasn't all it\Nwas cracked up to be, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My vision isn't\Nthe problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you all\Nexactly what I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of you\Nlistened to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I appreciate\Nyour efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer require\Nyour services.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! The animals have been\Nso excited for the sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they couldn't wait any longer.\NCan we take a look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um actually,\Nit's uh, not ready and--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry,\NFluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who\Nshould be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This didn't go at all\Nlike I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep tight, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be\NOK, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Everymouse has\Ngot to wait their turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. I thought I'd\Nhave a beautiful sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for you all to stay\Nin by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but I put my trust\Nin the wrong ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Fluttershy, I\Nknow you did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can make this work\Nhere. It'll be a bit... tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but with your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have these patients back\Non their paws in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without a sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!\NThese animals need me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to solve\Nthis once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If this little lady can\Ncrawl all the way here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from Western Equestria, I\Ncan find a way to build her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a safe place to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, everyone\Nback to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming,\Neverypony. As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,building the sanctuary\Ndidn't go quite as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.79,0:17:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right? Who'd\Nhave guessed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that Hard Hat wouldn't\Nbuild whatever you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have\Ninvited Dandy to help
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,if I thought he'd\Nact in such a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And Wrangler sure made\Na fool outta me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK. You were all\Njust trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know that letting all the\Nexperts go was the right call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going\Nto do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to re-build\Nthe sanctuary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and do it my way this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!\NThat's the spirit!\NYou show 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How about putting an\Nawesome flying course
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for the birds right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And a carrot-cake\Nstand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A library cave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony, STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you\Nsharing your thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need everypony\Nto respect mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Other ponies may be\Nexperts in their fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but animals are my\Nfield of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I say this\Nis what I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then this is what\Nneeds to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For the animals,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we should call\Nyou Flutterbold now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To get things back on\Ntrack, I called in a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from an old friend.\NHe'll be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said\Nno more "experts."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one expert I know I can\Ntrust to put the animals first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus there's nopony\Nbetter at building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. I heard somepony\Nneeds construction help
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for them critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Daddy McColt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We met each other back when the\Nmap called me and Fluttershy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Smokey Mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he certainly knows his stuff\Nwhen it comes to buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and caring for animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shucks, let's not stand\Naround talkin' about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's build us\Na sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm more excited than\Na beaver in a log pile!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. You can open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Sweetfeather\NSanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A safe and cozy retreat\Nfor every creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Fluttershy.\NThis is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you should have plenty\Nof room at the clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because once you've treated\Nthem, they can recover here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With my help, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Lola. We all\Nmove at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes all we need to do\Nis believe in our dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we finally\Nreach our goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,... we'll know that it was worth\Nwhat it took to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the view will be even\Nbetter than you imagined.
